code: import pandas as pd import re from sklearn.feature_extraction.text import TfidfVectorizer from sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split from xgboost import XGBClassifier from sklearn.metrics import roc_auc_score def preprocess(text): text = text.encode("utf-8").decode("unicode_escape")[1:-1] text = re.sub(r"[^\w\s]", "", text.lower()) return text def extract_text_features(comment): decoded = comment.encode("utf-8").decode("unicode_escape")[1:-1] exclamation = decoded.count("!") question = decoded.count("?") has_url = 1 if ("http://" in decoded) or ("https://" in decoded) else 0 uppercase = sum( 1 for word in decoded.split() if re.sub(r"[^A-Z]", "", word).isupper() and len(word) > 0 ) return exclamation, question, has_url, uppercase # Load and preprocess data train = pd.read_csv("./input/train.csv") test = pd.read_csv("./input/test.csv") train["clean_text"] = train["Comment"].apply(preprocess) test["clean_text"] = test["Comment"].apply(preprocess) # Extract text features train[["excl", "quest", "url", "uppercase"]] = ( train["Comment"].apply(extract_text_features).apply(pd.Series) ) test[["excl", "quest", "url", "uppercase"]] = ( test["Comment"].apply(extract_text_features).apply(pd.Series) ) # Extract date features for df in [train, test]: dates = df["Date"].str.replace("Z$", "+0000", regex=True) df["dt"] = pd.to_datetime(dates, format="%Y%m%d%H%M%S%z", errors="coerce") df["hour"] = df["dt"].dt.hour.fillna(-1) df["dow"] = df["dt"].dt.weekday.fillna(-1) df["date_missing"] = df["dt"].isna().astype(int) # TF-IDF features tfidf = TfidfVectorizer(max_features=5000, ngram_range=(1, 2)) X_train = tfidf.fit_transform(train["clean_text"]) X_test = tfidf.transform(test["clean_text"]) # Create feature matrices meta_features = [ "char_count", "word_count", "all_caps", "excl", "quest", "url", "uppercase", "hour", "dow", "date_missing", ] for i, df in enumerate([train, test]): df["char_count"] = df["clean_text"].str.len() df["word_count"] = df["clean_text"].str.split().str.len() df["all_caps"] = df["clean_text"].str.isupper().astype(int) X_train = pd.DataFrame.sparse.from_spmatrix(X_train) X_test = pd.DataFrame.sparse.from_spmatrix(X_test) X_train[meta_features] = train[meta_features] X_test[meta_features] = test[meta_features] # Model training with early stopping X_train_split, X_val, y_train_split, y_val = train_test_split( X_train, train["Insult"], test_size=0.2, random_state=42 ) model = XGBClassifier( n_estimators=1000, max_depth=6, learning_rate=0.05, tree_method="gpu_hist", eval_metric="auc", random_state=42, ) model.fit( X_train_split, y_train_split, early_stopping_rounds=20, eval_set=[(X_val, y_val)], verbose=False, ) # Create final model with best iteration params = model.get_params() params["n_estimators"] = model.best_iteration final_model = XGBClassifier(**params) final_model.fit(X_train, train["Insult"]) # Generate submission test_probs = final_model.predict_proba(X_test)[:, 1] pd.DataFrame({"Date": test.Date, "Comment": test.Comment, "Insult": test_probs}).to_csv( "./submission/submission.csv", index=False ) # Validation metric val_preds = final_model.predict_proba(X_val)[:, 1] print(f"Validation AUC: {roc_auc_score(y_val, val_preds):.4f}")
